overview.en: LEOOY Online travel platform is a one-stop travel service cultural platform of brand-new concept created by the Singapore Cultural Tourism Foundation to subvert the traditional tourism consumption ideas, and simply referred to as LEOOY.
overview.zh: 乐鸥在线文旅平台是新加坡文化旅游基金会全力打造的一个颠覆传统旅游消费观念的全新概念一站式的旅游服务文化交流平台，简称为乐鸥文旅平台。
